{"tid":2110112,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【打壓港台】遭葛博士狙擊後 港台拒再售《鏗鏘集》播映權予《蘋果》","createTime":"2020-07-15T16:09:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T16:48:28.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cd2e8670b1274d7ac11350e96a7fe9ec719a0ede","tid":2110112,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T16:09:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200715/LGQZRJP5PIPAZLOZB73ESOQVNU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200715%2FLGQZRJP5PIPAZLOZB73ESOQVNU%2F&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n3xTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=df2e32ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200715%2FLGQZRJP5PIPAZLOZB73ESOQVNU%2F&h=faabf01b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200715/LGQZRJP5PIPAZLOZB73ESOQVNU/</a><br />\n<br />\n民建聯「葛博士」葛珮帆5月於立法會議上點名批評為何香港電台容許《蘋果》平台播放《鏗鏘集》，事隔約2個月，《蘋果》接獲港台通知，決定完成現時合約後，不再向《蘋果》出售節目版權，即大概8月中後，《鏗鏘集》的往後集數將不能於「果燃台」播放。立法會議員毛孟靜形容「時機上太巧合」，相信港台因此承受一定政治壓力，才作出相關決定。港台發言人回應，只是望節目的點擊率集中他們的網上平台，否認與政治因素有關。"},{"pid":"ab7789b548b345f70dcffc2932c72ffedab1d4e4","tid":2110112,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T16:10:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"681b21ad8d3bd5681ba534272e601be07efa36ad","tid":2110112,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T16:12:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19cff45bef5e5e1df32c93b7270b61fccedc4b3d","tid":2110112,"uid"